title: The London Plane
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu rotates and is almost entirely vegetarian and vegan. Lunch menu feature soups and gourmet salads, about 75% of which are vegan or can be easily veganized. Whole foods. Big warm space with community tables for seating. Also has some housewares and wine for sale. A really rare veg find in the touristy Pioneer Square area.
